column1:
Christina E. Stephenson,

I hope this email finds you well. I'm a researcher with Govpack, an open-source technology that aggregates data on state- and local-level elected officials, allowing local newspapers to easily build candidate profiles and election guides. I'm in the process of data collection, and I wanted to make sure that I have complete, accurate data to fill out your profile.

This is the information I've collected:
• Name: Christina E. Stephenson
• Party: Nonpartisan
• State: OR
• Status: Challenger
• Office: OR Commissioner of the Bureau of Labor and Industries
• Campaign Email: cs4oregon@gmail.com
• Image: https://res.cloudinary.com/pies/images/h_552,w_475,c_pad,b_auto/christinastephenson/rkzlun46cgaujjd6gnpq/1906d4ef-62bd-402a-a5c2-fa99b4c3dbd1.jpg
• Campaign Website: http://christinastephenson.com/
• Campaign Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/christinastephensonfororegon
• Campaign Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/ChristinaStephensonforOregon/

I'm missing some information too, and I'm hoping you could help me fill in the gaps. I want to make sure that my data is equally robust for every public official.

Here's the information I'm still looking for:
• District
• Gender
• Education
• Occupation
• Other Email

• Date Of Birth
• Personal Website
